# id: KerberosRealm -> protected String maybeRemoveRealmName(final String principalName)
commentText: Usually principal names are in the form 'user/instance@REALM'. This method_removes '@REALM' part from the principal name if_{@link KerberosRealmSettings#SETTING_REMOVE_REALM_NAME} is {@code true} else_will return the input string.__@param principalName user principal name_@return username after removal of realm
codeText: protected String maybeRemoveRealmName(final String principalName) {_        if (this.removeRealmName) {_            int foundAtIndex = principalName.indexOf('@')__            if (foundAtIndex > 0) {_                return principalName.substring(0, foundAtIndex)__            }_        }_        return principalName__    }
